items.title: Recap: TB 1, NYY 8
items.description: Daily Recap: Michael Pineda took a perfect game into the 7th as the Yankees rolled to an 8-1 win over the Rays in their home opener
items.headline: Recap: TB 1, NYY 8
items.blurb: 4/10/17: Pineda leads Yanks to win in home opener

result.description: Aaron Judge homers (2) on a fly ball to left center field.
Chase Headley homers (2) on a line drive to right center field.
Umpire reviewed (home run), call on the field was overturned: Logan Morrison homers (2) on a fly ball to center field.
Umpire reviewed (home run), call on the field was upheld: Starlin Castro homers (1) on a fly ball to center field.   Chris Carter scores.

items.title: Recap: BOS 1, DET 2
items.description: Daily Recap: Justin Verlander allowed no earned runs in seven innings and Nicholas Castellanos hit the go-ahead single in the 8th
items.headline: Recap: BOS 1, DET 2
items.blurb: 4/10/17: Verlander hurls seven solid in Tigers' win

result.description: Brock Holt called out on strikes.
Ian Kinsler homers (2) on a fly ball to left center field.

items.title: Recap: OAK 2, KC 0
items.description: Daily Recap: Jharel Cotton tossed seven scoreless innings and Khris Davis supplied the offense with a two-run homer in the Athletics' win
items.headline: Recap: OAK 2, KC 0
items.blurb: 4/10/17: Cotton, Davis lead Athletics to win
